Downloads Databrary contants from API.

Source: R/assign_constants.R
assign_constants.Rd

Downloads Databrary contants from API.

assign_constants(vb = FALSE)

Arguments

vb

A Boolean value. If TRUE provides verbose output.

Value

A data frame with the constants.

Examples

assign_constants()
